     fhir:div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <code>urn:undefined</code><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFPersonIdentifierType.html\">VF_PersonIdentifierType</a></b></td></tr><tr><td>23</td><td/><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span>pat</td></tr><tr><td>IG</td><td/><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-v2-0203.html#v2-0203-MB\">MB</a></td></tr><tr><td>SY</td><td/><td><span title=\"EQUIVALENT\">~</span><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-v2-0203.html#v2-0203-SS\">SS</a></td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <code>http://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/C4BBIdentifierType</code><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFPersonIdentifierType.html\">VF_PersonIdentifierType</a></b></td></tr><tr><td>pat</td><td>Account number</td><td/></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-v2-0203.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v2-0203</code></a><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td><td><b><a href=\"ConceptMap-CMVFPersonIdentifierType.html\">VF_PersonIdentifierType</a></b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-v2-0203.html#v2-0203-MB\">MB</a></td><td>Member number</td><td>An identifier for the insured of an insurance policy (this insured always has a subscriber), usually assigned by the insurance carrier.</td><td/></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/5.3.0/CodeSystem-v2-0203.html#v2-0203-SS\">SS</a></td><td>Social Security Number</td><td>Social Security number</td><td/></tr>